sequenceDiagram
    title ReAct Agent 详细处理流程
    participant Client as Client/API
    participant Router as Configurable Router
    participant Context as ContextManager
    participant ReAct as ReAct Agent
    participant Exec as ExecutionCoordinator
    participant Tools as ToolRegistry
    participant KMS as KMS API
    participant Monitor as Perf/Error Monitor

    Note over Client,Monitor: ==== 阶段1: 请求接收与路由 ====
    Client->>Router: 查询请求(query, session_id)
    activate Router

    Router->>Context: 缓存查询(get_cache)
    activate Context
    Context-->>Router: 返回缓存结果(null或数据)
    deactivate Context

    alt 缓存命中
        Router-->>Client: 直接返回缓存答案
        Note over Router: 快速路径结束
    else 缓存未命中
        Router->>ReAct: 启动ReAct处理(query)
        activate ReAct

        Note over ReAct,Monitor: ==== 阶段2: ReAct循环处理 ====

        loop ReAct循环 [最大5次迭代]
            ReAct->>ReAct: Think: 分析当前状态，计划下一步
            Note right of ReAct: 生成思考日志<br/>判断是否需要继续

            ReAct->>Exec: 执行动作(action_plan)
            activate Exec

            Exec->>Tools: 调用工具(tool_name, params)
            activate Tools

            alt 工具类型判断
                opt 知识检索
                    Tools->>KMS: 知识查询(kms_search)
                    activate KMS
                    KMS-->>Tools: 检索结果
                    deactivate KMS
                opt 计算/推理
                    Tools->>Tools: 本地计算/推理
                opt 其他工具
                    Tools->>Tools: 执行专用工具
            end

            Tools-->>Exec: 工具执行结果
            deactivate Tools

            Exec-->>ReAct: 观察结果(observation)
            deactivate Exec

            ReAct->>ReAct: Observe: 评估结果，更新状态
            Note right of ReAct: 检查是否满足终止条件<br/>或达到最大迭代次数
        end

        Note over ReAct,Context: ==== 阶段3: 结果生成与缓存 ====
        ReAct->>Context: 保存结果到缓存(set_cache)
        activate Context
        Context-->>ReAct: 缓存确认
        deactivate Context

        ReAct-->>Router: 返回最终答案(answer, citations)
        deactivate ReAct

        Router-->>Client: 响应完整答案
    end

    Note over Router,Monitor: ==== 阶段4: 监控与清理 ====
    Monitor->>Monitor: 记录性能指标(各阶段耗时)
    Monitor->>Monitor: 错误统计与告警(如有)

    deactivate Router
    Note over Client,Monitor: ==== 流程结束 ====
